Package org.schabi.newpipe.extractor

Class MultiInfoItemsCollector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.schabi.newpipe.extractor.InfoItemsCollector<InfoItem,​InfoItemExtractor>
      • org.schabi.newpipe.extractor.MultiInfoItemsCollector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Collector<InfoItem,​InfoItemExtractor>
    public class MultiInfoItemsCollector
extends InfoItemsCollector<InfoItem,​InfoItemExtractor>
    A collector that can handle many extractor types, to be used when a list contains items of different types (e.g. search)

    This collector can handle the following extractor types:

    • StreamInfoItemExtractor
    • ChannelInfoItemExtractor
    • PlaylistInfoItemExtractor
    Calling extract(InfoItemExtractor) or InfoItemsCollector.commit(InfoItemExtractor) with any other extractor type will raise an exception.
